This repository contains course materials and SQL practice work for the AUCA Database course.

## About This Repository

The project is focused on relational database fundamentals and PostgreSQL practice, including:

- database setup and schema creation
- table design, keys, and constraints
- CRUD operations and querying
- joins, aggregate functions, and advanced SQL
- transactions, import/export, and backup workflows

## Academic Disclaimer

All materials in this repository are prepared for coursework and learning purposes. SQL scripts should be executed only in your own local or authorized academic environments.

Do not use these scripts against systems you do not own or do not have permission to access.

