## Labs (Exact Naming)

Each lab folder uses this naming pattern:

- `labs/lab-N/index.md`
- `labs/lab-N/lab.sql`
- `labs/lab-N/<lab-topic>.docx`

Lab folders present in the repository:

- `lab-1`, `lab-2`, `lab-3`, `lab-4`, `lab-5`, `lab-6`, `lab-7`, `lab-8`, `lab-9`
- `lab-10`, `lab-11`, `lab-12`, `lab-13`, `lab-14`, `lab-15`, `lab-16`, `lab-17`

## University Example Schema Files

These database schema and sample query files are located in `labs/`:

- `labs/university.sql` - Create university database
- `labs/departments.sql` - Department table definitions
- `labs/positions.sql` - Position table definitions
- `labs/employees.sql` - Employee table definitions
- `labs/students.sql` - Student table definitions
- `labs/courses.sql` - Course table definitions
- `labs/enrollments.sql` - Enrollment table definitions
- `labs/query.sql` - Sample query examples
- `labs/ER_diagram.png` - Entity-relationship diagram

